      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out! I've babied this car since day one, and it still has that brand-new feel and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for total perfection, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
