    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a definitive example of Bavarian engineering. At its heart is the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a fully serviced double-VANOS system for razor-sharp throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock, ensuring maximum power delivery to the rear wheels. The chassis has been meticulously preserved, including proactive subframe reinforcement and a suspension refresh utilizing Bilstein dampers for neutralized body roll. This vehicle retains its factory-original paint depth and an immaculate interior with zero bolster wear on the Nappa leather. Documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive service history make this a turnkey masterpiece for the performance purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
