      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive masterpiece that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, free from swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, reflecting like a mirror under any light. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery still carries that distinct new-car aroma, with every stitch and bolster appearing as if it just left the factory floor. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule documented in a comprehensive binder of service records. Every button, dial, and electronic feature operates with precision. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
